* Start-up Pattern
pa=*

* Sort Value
s=2

* Tree Saving
t=1

* Tag Counter Location
tl=2

* Screen Blank Time Out Value (minutes)
to=3

* File Viewer
v=ezv

* Pause After DOS Command
w=1

* Confirm on Exit
xc=1

